subscript
Element


subscript
&subscript.purpose;


&subscript.synopsis.gen;
Description



Subscript identifies text that is to be displayed as a subscript
when rendered.


Processing expectations


&format.inline; Subscripts are usually printed in a smaller font and shifted
down with respect to the baseline.




&subscript.parents.gen;
&subscript.children.gen;

